# --description--

The menu looks good, but other than the coffee beans background image, it is mainly just text.

Under the `Coffee` heading, add an image using the url `/images/coffee.jpg`. Give the image an `alt` value of `coffee icon`.

# --hints--

You should have an `<img>` tag. Remember that `img` elements are self-closing.

```js
assert($('img').length === 1);
```

Your `img` element should have a `src` attribute of `/images/coffee.jpg`.

```js
assert($('img').attr('src') === '/images/coffee.jpg');
```

Your `img` element should have an `alt` attribute of `coffee icon`.

```js
assert($('img').attr('alt').match(/coffee icon/i));
```

